1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v3 7.5
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity
Vendor: Hitachi Energy
Equipment: AFS650, AFS660, AFS665, AFS670, AFS675, AFS677, AFR677
